[2026-05-28 08:13:46] [DEBUG   ] discord.gateway: For Shard ID None: WebSocket Event: {'t': 'MESSAGE_CREATE', 's': 152, 'op': 0, 'd': {'type': 0, 'tts': False, 'timestamp': '2026-05-28T14:13:47.346000+00:00', 'pinned': False, 'nonce': '1509560322329935872', 'mentions': [{'username': 'alt_0ne', 'public_flags': 0, 'primary_guild': {'tag': 'OoTR', 'identity_guild_id': '274180765816848384', 'identity_enabled': True, 'badge': '79dae93b4acc456cc8aaf6ed2accc540'}, 'member': {'roles': ['1382116456443154542'], 'premium_since': None, 'pending': False, 'nick': 'Hoshirō', 'mute': False, 'joined_at': '2025-07-19T17:32:18.785000+00:00', 'flags': 0, 'deaf': False, 'communication_disabled_until': None, 'banner': None, 'avatar': None}, 'id': '478791535660630026', 'global_name': '( ͡° ͜ʖ ͡°) TheOne', 'display_name_styles': None, 'discriminator': '0', 'collectibles': None, 'clan': {'tag': 'OoTR', 'identity_guild_id': '274180765816848384', 'identity_enabled': True, 'badge': '79dae93b4acc456cc8aaf6ed2accc540'}, 'avatar_decoration_data': None, 'avatar': '493d6df3cbae05c839449f8824b96724'}, {'username': 'pohmg', 'public_flags': 0, 'primary_guild': None, 'member': {'roles': ['1382116456443154542'], 'premium_since': None, 'pending': False, 'nick': 'Arnish', 'mute': False, 'joined_at': '2025-06-10T16:24:38.772000+00:00', 'flags': 0, 'deaf': False, 'communication_disabled_until': None, 'banner': None, 'avatar': None}, 'id': '1213285558810312754', 'global_name': 'Hunter ♥', 'display_name_styles': None, 'discriminator': '0', 'collectibles': None, 'clan': None, 'avatar_decoration_data': None, 'avatar': '52d0ff2cd7dac2dc63a9bbe9d3cad8bb'}], 'mention_roles': ['1382116456443154542'], 'mention_everyone': False, 'member': {'roles': ['1382116348783497337'], 'premium_since': None, 'pending': False, 'nick': 'Dm', 'mute': False, 'joined_at': '2025-06-10T16:13:55.457000+00:00', 'flags': 0, 'deaf': False, 'communication_disabled_until': None, 'banner': None, 'avatar': None}, 'id': '1509560323286241342', 'flags': 0, 'embeds': [], 'edited_timestamp': None, 'content': 'Ok <@&1382116456443154542> I came to some decisions last night. \nWe now have a 5 person party again, with people I have full faith are going to stick around for a while. With that in mind the final boss of any campaign is actually scheduling conflicts. \nWe have all set aside time each week, and not a small amount of time either, to play this game together. It’s not fair if one person calls in and it ruins everyone else’s night. With that being said we’re all adults with responsibilities and children to take care of, so things happen. Going forward, if the party knows at least 3 days in advance that you are unable to make it to a session, we can make other plans. If you let everyone know in less time, we will proceed with the session without you. So far no one has had this issue in this party so I’m not super worried that this will change anything. \nIf you can’t make it more than 2 weeks in a row, sessions will continue without you. Again, I don’t think this is unjust or is going to affect us. \nI am feeling better about dnd and getting back into the flow, and being able to schedule my homework better than previously. With that in mind I would like to move back to weekly dnd. I do want to say though that if <@478791535660630026> or <@1213285558810312754> are still interested in running I will happily move back to bi-weekly to allow you that option.', 'components': [], 'channel_type': 0, 'channel_id': '1382030507771953233', 'author': {'username': 'kingdomtily', 'public_flags': 0, 'primary_guild': {'tag': 'AP', 'identity_guild_id': '731205301247803413', 'identity_enabled': True, 'badge': '1935451f265a42d57241c7bcc9555abe'}, 'id': '363021684158103562', 'global_name': 'Kingdom Tily', 'display_name_styles': None, 'discriminator': '0', 'collectibles': None, 'clan': {'tag': 'AP', 'identity_guild_id': '731205301247803413', 'identity_enabled': True, 'badge': '1935451f265a42d57241c7bcc9555abe'}, 'avatar_decoration_data': None, 'avatar': '32195f7d881d20be7d637264d84391b7'}, 'attachments': [], 'guild_id': '1382030027008512062'}}
