[2026-05-28 08:13:49] [DEBUG   ] discord.gateway: For Shard ID None: WebSocket Event: {'t': 'MESSAGE_CREATE', 's': 153, 'op': 0, 'd': {'type': 0, 'tts': False, 'timestamp': '2026-05-28T14:13:50.367000+00:00', 'pinned': False, 'nonce': '1509560334954790912', 'mentions': [], 'mention_roles': [], 'mention_everyone': False, 'member': {'roles': ['1382116348783497337'], 'premium_since': None, 'pending': False, 'nick': 'Dm', 'mute': False, 'joined_at': '2025-06-10T16:13:55.457000+00:00', 'flags': 0, 'deaf': False, 'communication_disabled_until': None, 'banner': None, 'avatar': None}, 'id': '1509560335957229788', 'flags': 0, 'embeds': [], 'edited_timestamp': None, 'content': 'Dnd sessions start at 6:30 and are over at 10:30. if we end early, it’s either because I didn’t have time to prepare the things you are about to experience or I want to leave the session at a cliff hanger. Please let your people know this. I have ended early a few times recently and I think that has set the expectation that it is over at 9. If that doesn’t work for people, please let me know. \nWith how little time we have for sessions, I propose that we eat for about 15 minutes and jump in. If you are running late, you may miss a portion of the session. We don’t play for huge sessions so missing an hour waiting on someone is a huge blow\n\n\nWith all that being said, I want to re-iterate that there’s no one here I see as a “problem player”, however I think it’s important to have clear boundaries and expectations, everyone knows the rules so no one will feel blindsided if they get affected by one. If any of these feel unfair please let me know. I will work with yall. Thank you and see you Monday', 'components': [], 'channel_type': 0, 'channel_id': '1382030507771953233', 'author': {'username': 'kingdomtily', 'public_flags': 0, 'primary_guild': {'tag': 'AP', 'identity_guild_id': '731205301247803413', 'identity_enabled': True, 'badge': '1935451f265a42d57241c7bcc9555abe'}, 'id': '363021684158103562', 'global_name': 'Kingdom Tily', 'display_name_styles': None, 'discriminator': '0', 'collectibles': None, 'clan': {'tag': 'AP', 'identity_guild_id': '731205301247803413', 'identity_enabled': True, 'badge': '1935451f265a42d57241c7bcc9555abe'}, 'avatar_decoration_data': None, 'avatar': '32195f7d881d20be7d637264d84391b7'}, 'attachments': [], 'guild_id': '1382030027008512062'}}
