[2026-05-29 10:25:51] [DEBUG   ] discord.gateway: For Shard ID None: WebSocket Event: {'t': 'MESSAGE_CREATE', 's': 224, 'op': 0, 'd': {'type': 0, 'tts': False, 'timestamp': '2026-05-29T16:25:52.046000+00:00', 'pinned': False, 'nonce': '1509955948750307328', 'mentions': [], 'mention_roles': [], 'mention_everyone': False, 'member': {'roles': ['1382116348783497337'], 'premium_since': None, 'pending': False, 'nick': 'Dm', 'mute': False, 'joined_at': '2025-06-10T16:13:55.457000+00:00', 'flags': 0, 'deaf': False, 'communication_disabled_until': None, 'banner': None, 'avatar': None}, 'id': '1509955949752750231', 'flags': 0, 'embeds': [], 'edited_timestamp': None, 'content': 'Aight boys. It’s been a while. I have come to a decision about weekly assignments. \nA) I do not enjoy reminding people to do them\nB) when I feel like I am pushing people to do them I feel like a teacher with a student that never turns in their work on time. I hate this. \nC) this is designed to help you. These are here to help you expand your experience. These are so that those of you who desire it can experience dnd as more than a game, but be transported to another world and experience the closest thing that this world has to an alternate reality. They’re not for me. \nD) we’re adults. We each have the ability and maturity to decide what we want to do. \n\nWith all of that in mind, I am done asking for assignments to be done. I will not beg people to do their assignments. They are not required. But I will reward the people who do them, as it IS an extra thing you are doing for the game. Whether it’s money, experience, or possibly even magic items, the reward will be revealed at the same time as the assignment.', 'components': [], 'channel_type': 0, 'channel_id': '1382039585676329171', 'author': {'username': 'kingdomtily', 'public_flags': 0, 'primary_guild': {'tag': 'AP', 'identity_guild_id': '731205301247803413', 'identity_enabled': True, 'badge': '1935451f265a42d57241c7bcc9555abe'}, 'id': '363021684158103562', 'global_name': 'Kingdom Tily', 'display_name_styles': None, 'discriminator': '0', 'collectibles': None, 'clan': {'tag': 'AP', 'identity_guild_id': '731205301247803413', 'identity_enabled': True, 'badge': '1935451f265a42d57241c7bcc9555abe'}, 'avatar_decoration_data': None, 'avatar': '32195f7d881d20be7d637264d84391b7'}, 'attachments': [], 'guild_id': '1382030027008512062'}}
